---
title: Creamy Lemon & Double Prawn Orecchiette with Parsley & Chilli Flakes
description: A seafood pasta feels fancy without even trying and we think a squeeze of zesty lemon juice with these prawns is enough to earn a five star rating for this orecchiette dish. We’ll let you be the judge.
